snippet.title: Sid Meier's Pirates!: Live the Life (PC) (2004) Video Game US Trailer
snippet.description:
US Trailer for the Windows version of the Sid Meier's Pirates!: Live the Life video game, remake of the 1987 original Sid Meier's Pirates video game.
